Details 1950-1959
1940

 
153.
Torino (Stadio Municipale "Benito Mussolini") - Sunday, 3 March 1940 - h. 14,30
ITALIA - SWITZERLAND      1-1 (1-1)           Friendly
ITALIA:  A. Olivieri (Torino) 22, Foni (Juventus) 19, Rava (Juventus) 25, 
            Depetrini (Juventus) 8, Andreolo (Bologna) 24, Locatelli (Ambrosiana
                      - Inter) 20, G. Neri (Genoa) 3, Arcari IV (Genoa) 1, Piola (Lazio)
                        26 (cap.), Corbelli (Venezia) 1, Ferraris II (Ambrosiana - Inter) 7.
                           Coach: V. Pozzo. 
SWITZERLAND:    Ballabio, Minelli (cap.), A. Lehmann , Springer, Andreoli, Bichsel,
                          Bickel, A. Abegglen, Monnard, Amadò, G. Aebi. Federation's Technical
                                  Commission.
Referee: Beranek (Austria).
Scorers: 20' Bickel (S), 36' Corbelli
Attendance: 40,000

154.
