                Silva, Zarra, Hernandez (46' Cesar), Gainza. Coach: Eizaguirre.
ITALIA:         V. Bacigalupo (Torino) 5, Ballarin (Torino) 9, Becattini (Genoa) 1,
                   Annovazzi (Milan) 5, Rigamonti (Torino) 3, Castigliano (Torino) 7,
                             Menti II (Torino) 7, Lorenzi (Inter) 1, Amadei (Inter) 1, V. Mazzola
                                   (Torino) 12 (cap.), Carapellese (Milan) 6. Federation's Technical
                                            Commission.
Referee: Ling (England).
Scorers: 9' Lorenzi, 34' Gainza rig. (S), 48' Carapellese, 50' Amadei
Attendance: 80,000
Note: Last match before the Superga airplane crash. At 86' Gainza missed a penalty.

